# Keep the Docker build context small and cache-friendly. The custom
# Superset Dockerfile only needs apps/superset-plugins/ and docker/superset/,
# so most of the repo is dead weight at build time and worse, busts caches.

# VCS
.git
.gitignore
.github

# Node / pnpm
# DO NOT exclude pnpm-lock.yaml: apps/api/Dockerfile and apps/web/Dockerfile
# both `COPY pnpm-lock.yaml` for `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`. The custom
# Superset Dockerfile in docker/superset/ uses plain npm and ignores it, so
# keeping the file in the build context is harmless there.
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store

# Build outputs
**/dist
**/build
**/lib
**/.next
**/.turbo

# Editor / OS
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.swp

# Tests / coverage
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results

# Docs / project files unrelated to the Superset image
docs
README.md
*.md
!docker/superset/README.md
!apps/superset-plugins/README.md

# Claude / agent state
.claude
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
